title: Picget PhotoShine 5.5 + Serial Key [SadeemPC].zip
description:
Picget PhotoShine 5.5

PhotoShine gives you an easy way to make photo collage by adding your photo into different beautiful templates. For example, you can add your photo into a classical love style template, a pink girl style template, a baby cartoon template, or a magazine cover template etc by just one click in PhotoShine.	

Key Features: 
1) Easy to use
Just one click, you can add your photo into the template which you like.

2) 9 themes (styles), more than 680 beautiful templates included.
The 9 themes are: GIRL, BABY, LOVE, BOARD, DREAM, MAGAZINE, FESTIVAL, FRAME and OTHER.
There are more than 680 templates included in PhotoShine, which means you have more than 680 choices to make your photo more attractive.
